<div class="page-faq pt-nav">

  {%- comment -%} Hero {%- endcomment -%}
  <div style="position:relative;height:40vh;min-height:300px;overflow:hidden;">
    <img
      src="{{ 'customer-service.jpg' | asset_url }}"
      alt="FAQ"
      style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;"
    >
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:2rem;">
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4.5rem);color:#fff;margin-bottom:1rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.1rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);max-width:500px;">Everything you need to know</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} FAQ Accordion {%- endcomment -%}
  <section style="padding:5rem 0;background:#fff;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="faq-list">

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            How long does shipping take?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Orders are processed within 1–3 business days. Standard US delivery takes 5–7 business days and is free on every order — no minimum. Express (2–3 days) and overnight options are available at checkout. See our <a href="/pages/shipping" style="color:var(--color-accent);">Shipping page</a> for full details.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            Is shipping really free?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes — free standard shipping on every US order, no minimum spend. Express and overnight upgrades are available at checkout if you need it faster.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            How do I track my order?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>As soon as your order ships, we send a confirmation email with a tracking link. If you can't find it, check your spam folder or <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:var(--color-accent);">contact us</a> with your order number and we'll resend it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            What is your return policy?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We accept returns within <strong>30 days</strong> of delivery on unused items in their original packaging. See our full <a href="/pages/returns" style="color:var(--color-accent);">Returns page</a> for the step-by-step process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            What if my item arrives damaged or defective?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Email <a href="mailto:support@mammothstore.com" style="color:var(--color-accent);">support@mammothstore.com</a> within 7 days of delivery with your order number and a photo of the issue. We'll send a replacement or issue a refund — no restocking fee, no back-and-forth.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            Can I change or cancel my order?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>If your order hasn't shipped yet, we can usually update the address or cancel it. Email us as soon as possible at <a href="mailto:support@mammothstore.com" style="color:var(--color-accent);">support@mammothstore.com</a> with your order number. Once an order is in transit we can't modify it, but you can always return it under our 30-day policy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            How are your products curated?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Every MAMMOTH product is hand-picked. We test, review specs, and check real customer feedback before a product makes it into the store. If something doesn't hold up to daily use, it doesn't make the cut.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            Do you ship internationally?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Right now we focus on shipping within the United States so we can keep delivery fast and free. International shipping is on the roadmap — follow us or sign up for our newsletter to hear when it launches.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            What payment methods do you accept?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We accept all major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover), PayPal, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and Shop Pay. Checkout is secured end-to-end by Shopify.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            Is checkout secure?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes. All payments run through Shopify's PCI-compliant checkout with SSL encryption. We never see or store your full card details.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
            How do I contact customer support?
            <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@mammothstore.com" style="color:var(--color-accent);">support@mammothstore.com</a> or use the <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:var(--color-accent);">contact form</a>. A real person reads every message and we reply within 24 hours on business days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style>
.faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
.faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e0da; }
.faq-question {
  width: 100%;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  padding: 1.5rem 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 1rem;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  text-align: left;
  cursor: pointer;
  color: var(--color-text);
}
.faq-question:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
.faq-icon { flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform 0.25s; }
.faq-question[aria-expanded="true"] .faq-icon { transform: rotate(180deg); }
.faq-answer {
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s;
}
.faq-answer p {
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.8;
  padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  margin: 0;
}
.faq-answer.open { max-height: 500px; }
</style>

<script>
document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(function(btn) {
  btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
    var expanded = btn.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
    var answer = btn.nextElementSibling;
    btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', !expanded);
    answer.classList.toggle('open', !expanded);
  });
});
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ Page",
  "tag": "div"
}
{% endschema %}
